[These reports paint a more favorable account of pet ownership in China
(and Beijing in particular) than some past reports. It is likely that the
measures presently being implemented in Beijing and elsewhere are a
response to the imminence of the XXIX Olympiad in Beijing in 2008. - Mod.CP]
